conbody.p: Create a center mark associated with a selected circle, arc, or polyarc.

section.title: Methods to create a center mark
section.p: There is one method to begin creating a center mark:

dlentry.dd: Begin creating a center mark by selecting a circle, arc or polyarc. Depending on the current value of the , the center mark is drawn with or without extension lines. Additional center settings further control the appearance of centermarks.
The center mark is associative, so when the arc or circle is moved or resized, the centermark follows.
